# 3. 旅行の朝は

Tsukasa: Alright, I've finished my daily run, and I have everything packed for our trip!
Tsukasa: What else do I have left to do...? Oh, I still haven't done my morning strength exercises!
Tsukasa: That was a close one! I'll need to do those to ensure that we have a wonderful day!
Tsukasa: Starting with pushups! Hmph! Hmph! Hnnnnnnng!!
Mother: Morning, Tsukasa. You seem more excited than usual this morning.
Tsukasa: Morning, Mom!
Tsukasa: That's because Saki and I are going on a trip for the first time in a very long while! I can't contain my excitement!
Tsukasa: That reminds me. I made a special breakfast today as a way to boost my luck. Have some if you like, Mom.
Mother: Oh, thank you. I hope you two enjoy your trip.
Tsukasa: We will!
Tsukasa: Wait, look at the time... I need to wake Saki...
Tsukasa: *Inhale*
Tsukasa: Sakiiiiii!!!!! It's moooorrrnnniiiinnnggg!!!!!!
Saki's Voice: Huh?! Tsukasa?!
Saki's Voice: You don't have to shout! I'm already up!
Tsukasa's Voice: Oh, you're checking to see if you've packed properly! Did you make sure to include bug repellent?
Saki's Voice: Yeah! It's in this bag...
Saki's Voice: No, it's not...! Wait, where'd it go?!
Mother: Hehe. You two are so excited.
Shiho: (Mhm... It's morning already...?)
Shiho: (Huh...? My alarm went off earlier than usual...)
Shiho: (Oh, right... Today's...)
Rin: <Rin-Rin-Riiiin☆ It's morning!>
Shiho: Whoa...! You scared me...
Rin: <Wakey wakey, Shih!>
Shiho: Relax... I'm already awake.
Rin: <What? But you're still snuggled up in your bed! You're gonna be late if you don't start getting ready soon!>
Shiho: Okay, I'll get up. There's no need to rush.
Rin: <Hehe. I'm so excited about visiting that cafe, picking fruits and seeing some pretty leaves!>
Rin: <Thanks again for agreeing to let me go with you today, Shih♪>
Shiho: I mean, you looked like you really wanted to go the other day when I told you about this trip...
Shiho: I think Shizuku and Tsukasa won't notice as long as you don't pop out too often.
Rin: <Right! I should be fine since I can just sneakily watch from your pocket or Sakki's☆>
Shizuku's Voice: Shii?
Shizuku's Voice: Shii, are you awake? We're going to be late if you don't get up soon.
Shiho: I'm already up.
Shizuku: Morning, Shii. I'm glad we were both able to wake up early like we planned.
Shiho: You didn't have to worry about that. I had an alarm set for today.
Shiho: Also, Shizuku, you've got bed head...
Shizuku: Huh?
Shiho: Look, around your right ear. This bit of hair's sticking up.
Shizuku: What? But I thought I got it all... I-I'll go fix it now...!
Shiho: *Sigh* She's so careless when it comes to these things.
Rin: <She might've been distracted because she's just that excited about today. That happens to me a lot!>
Shiho: Yeah, you also seem like the type to forget about fixing your bed head before going somewhere.
Rin: <What?! R-Really?!>
Rin: <But you've also gotten so excited about something that you forgot about other stuff, right?!>
Shiho: I don't think so...
Rin: <O-Or ended up just spinning your wheels...?>
Shiho: Nope.
Rin: <Y-Yeah, I probably am barking up the wrong tree...>
Rin: <But you are excited about this trip, right? I mean, you kept checking the weather forecast yesterday.>
Shiho: Of course I kept checking the forecast. Depending on the weather, we would've had to pack differently.
Shiho: But I am glad that it's supposed to be nice out today.
Rin: <Oh...>
Rin: <Yeah! So let's have lots of fun on today's trip♪>
Shiho: Yeah, within reason...
